title: Ruffage Natural Foods
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sandwich and small health food shop walking distance from Waikiki Beach. Veg except for turkey and tuna. Each day a special plus vegan choices including tofu vegan omelette, taro burgers, tempeh, veggie burrito, chili dogs, chili with rice, and smoothies. Limited seating.
